{"tid":2427803,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"香港/移民外國/回流香港/台灣人 呢到等緊你加入","createTime":"2021-03-01T05:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T14:24:41.000Z","uid":9178,"like":10,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b30f4efc9eced403a9a87c8bf88af4f72f96430","tid":2427803,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">香港人<br />\n喺外國嘅香港人<br />\n回流香港嘅香港人<br />\n台灣人</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個谷都歎迎你 交友無分界限<br />\n<br />\n不論你好悶，係外國冇人傾計，返嚟香港後冇朋友，台灣人想認識香港文化，呢到都十分啱你。<span class=\"gold\">話題圍繞國家，個人，日常生活，總之咩都講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n呢到絕不強逼你出聚，自由出聚。<span class=\"gold\">呢到啲外國巴絲已經自行成功搞過聚啦</span><br />\n<br />\n暫時谷中24小時都有人 因為唔同國家嘅人都有（<span class=\"gold\">歐洲+香港+本地台灣人</span>）<br />\n<br />\n唔洗擔心時差，總有人陪到你<br />\n<br />\nset咗只可填一次 所以要登入 唔想人重複又重複咁填<br />\n如果擔心嘅就唔好入 個人選擇 <br />\n絕對唔會揀人加 所以歡迎入完再入 <br />\n加人速度慢 唔好意思要耐心等等<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">P.s 身處英國嘅谷友強烈表示希望多啲英國jj加入，佢哋等緊你哋入嚟</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/KbEdDZYPmTcz45dt5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FKbEdDZYPmTcz45dt5&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Xfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=1537f0a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/KbEdDZYPmTcz45dt5</a>"},{"pid":"bdb3d1c046a585ce4d59202d23d768a812512aa7","tid":2427803,"uid":9178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"唔接受入嚟潛水做cd-rom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64a425687d12143155dd09a03fb554a33eb5045","tid":2427803,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a4291792b48347244e1357ddf3b19f5396c7a4","tid":2427803,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"